OL,5,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FA woman suffers with chronic back
OL,7,     Fpain since giving birth to her
OL,8,     Ftwins five years ago. During the
OL,9,     Fprocedure, Hannah was given an
OL,10,     Fepidural that caused nerve damage
OL,11,     Fin her spine.
OL,12,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,14,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,15,     Funder the microscope. 84-year-old
OL,16,     FTerry, comes in with a
OL,17,     Fbadly-broken ankle and fears he
OL,18,     Fmay never dance again.
